          <funding>
              <para>PlantNet is an open consortium founded by four French research organizations (CIRAD, Inria, INRAE, IRD) and supported by Agropolis Fondation. The two main funding resources are: (i) the annual contribution of the members of the consortium, (ii) donations from the end-users of PlantNet application (&gt;10 million users).</para>
